In this section, as well as in the 18 and 33. those small vessels that
sailed on the sea of , are called by Josephus, i.e. plainly ships;
so that we need not wander at our evangelists, who still call them ships;
nor ought we to render them boats, as some do, Their number was in all
230, as we learn from our author elsewhere. Jewish War. B. II. ch. 21.
sect. 8.
